OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA drink-driver has been jailed after
OL,7,Fkilling a "beloved mum" in a crash in
OL,8,FYate.
OL,10,FAshley Billing hit mum-of-four Rebecca
OL,11,FAshmead in Kennedy Way in March 2023
OL,12,Fand drove off.
OL,14,FMs Ashmead, who was known to her loved
OL,15,Fones as Bex, died at the scene - while
OL,16,Fpolice managed to track Billings down
OL,17,Fafter identifying his licence plate
OL,18,Fand front bumper, which came off
OL,19,Fduring the collision.
