OL,3,CDrink-driver jailed after killing
OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,FThe 39-year-old was arrested shortly
OL,7,Fafterwards and it was established he
OL,8,Fhad been driving under the influence
OL,9,Fof alcohol.
OL,11,FHe pleaded guilty to causing death
OL,12,Fwithout due care and attention while
OL,13,Fover the limit, causing death by
OL,14,Fdriving while disqualified and causing
OL,15,Fdeath by driving a vehicle in which
OL,16,Fthe driver is unlicensed/uninsured at
OL,17,FBristol Crown Court today (9 January).
