OL,3,CDrink-driver jailed after killing
OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,FHe was jailed for nine years, reduced
OL,7,Ffrom 12 years for his guilty plea. He
OL,8,Fhas also been banned from driving for
OL,9,F10 years.
OL,11,F'Our lives have been utterly
OL,12,Fdestroyed' - family statement
OL,14,FIn a statement by Ms Ashmead's family,
OL,15,Fthey said: "As a family, we are
OL,16,Frelieved the person responsible for
OL,17,Ftaking our beloved mum and sister from
OL,18,Fus has finally been sentenced.
