OL,3,CDrink-driver jailed after killing
OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"While no amount of time in prison
OL,7,Fwill ever change the fact that our
OL,8,Flives have been utterly destroyed by
OL,9,Fhis actions, we are grateful to have
OL,10,Fsome semblance of closure.
OL,12,F"Bex was the most selfless, caring,
OL,13,Ffun, hardworking and supportive person
OL,14,Fand her loss has devastated all her
OL,15,Ffamily, friends and the wider
OL,16,Fcommunity.
