OL,3,CDrink-driver jailed after killing
OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,F"We thank the police and CPS for their
OL,7,Fwork on her case, and to everyone
OL,8,Faround us who has given support and
OL,9,Fkind words, while continuing to
OL,10,Frespect our much-needed privacy.
OL,12,F"We hope that this traumatic event may
OL,13,Fcause people to be aware of the
OL,14,Fpotential impact of their own driving
OL,15,Fand consider taking a more active
OL,16,Fapproach in preventing others from
OL,17,Fdriving in situations where they may
OL,18,Fbe impaired."
