OL,4,C'beloved mum' in hit-and-run
OL,6,FDesignated Collision Investigation
OL,7,FOfficer Anthony Hall, from Avon and
OL,8,FSomerset Police, said: "Billing's
OL,9,Fselfish actions that day took away a
OL,10,Fmother from her children and that is
OL,11,Funforgivable.
OL,13,F"I hope this sentence will serve as a
OL,14,Freminder to for people to think twice
OL,15,Fbefore getting behind the wheel and
OL,16,Fwill give Bex's family some closure as
OL,17,Fthey continue to come to terms with
OL,18,Ftheir loss."
